src:
Byåsen vant historisk kamp foran over 7000 tilskuere: – Jeg er laget for disse anledningene
02 Nov 2019, 16:59 by Even Berthelsen
Ida Alstad viste klasse og rutine da hun scoret den nye storstuens aller første mål og sikret seieren.

Byåsen – Molde 26 – 21 (13–9)
text:
Byåsen won a historic match in front of over 7000 spectators: - I am made for these occasions
02 Nov 2019, 16:59 by Even Berthelsen
Ida Alstad showed class and routine as she scored the new first room's very first goal and secured the victory.

Byåsen - Molde 26 - 21 (13–9)
